race.comment: ISTOLEA MERC (3) strengthened over the break and is expected to run out the 1400m today. Attacked the line when second over 1250m at Canterbury in BM78 class. A repeat effort will see him prove hard to hold out from the good gate. ROLLING MAGIC (4) progressive gelding who sprinted quickly on resumption when a close-up second over 1300m at Rosehill in Midway class. Can go on with it this prep and is expected to play a leading role today. REMATCH (5) durable gelding who will relish the weight drop second-up. Went under narrowly with the 62kg when second over 1400m at Armidale.  Kept up to the mark with a 1000m trial and Bullock sticks. Will be charging late. RHYTHM IS A DANCER (7) is undefeated at this track and his best form is over this trip. Not far away again when third over 1400m at Armidale. Strays in the mix.
